Class CollectionFactory.ThreadSafeConditionalCopySet<T>

    All Implemented Interfaces:

    CollectionFactory

    public static class CollectionFactory.ThreadSafeConditionalCopySet<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Set<T>
    this class behaves like ConditionalCopySet except it is designed to be threadsafe; multiple thread access is regulated by a readwritelock; modifications will create a copy based on SyncSet.
